*Odeljenje* je prvo korak ka uspehu u školi. (The class is the first step towards success in school.)

Direktor je posetio svako *odeljenje* u školi. (The director visited every class in the school.)

Učenici su se sastali na hodniku ispred *odeljenja*. (The students met in the hallway outside the class.)

Deca su se igrala u dvorištu ispred *odeljenja*. (The children were playing in the courtyard outside the class.)

Nastavnik je ušao u *odeljenje* sa pločom punom zadataka. (The teacher entered the class with a board full of tasks.)

*Odeljenje* je radilo ceo dan na projektu. (The class worked all day on the project.)